The paper also discusses the constraints on the adversary, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The algorithm involves communication between processors, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). Overall, the paper covers topics that are relevant to multiple sub-categories in computer science, but the most relevant ones are likely cs.DC and cs.DS.
